What is an example of a song from each of these popular genres that you like?
From pop, I enjoy “Shake It Off” by Taylor Swift because it has a positive message about overcoming failure and moving on with life. From rock, I like “Bohemian Rhapsody” by Queen for its dramatic range of styles from soft to hard rock. Hip-hop/rap songs that I appreciate include “Jump Around” by House of Pain due to its energetic beats and fun lyrics. Country music that appeals to me is “Highway Man” by Johnny Cash because of its poetic storytelling and poignant themes about life on the road.
